{"tid":2008074,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一句返工俾人屌完即刻發奮既說話","createTime":"2020-05-08T18:08:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T04:30:33.000Z","uid":126046,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8f45f9aba2c12df488e36b4caae51aa4528bcee7","tid":2008074,"uid":126046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T18:08:39.000Z","msg":"做錯野俾人屌緊架啦<br />\n又或者啲野做出黎人地唔滿意 都俾人屌<br />\n基本上返工返多幾年菊花都變太陽花<br />\n分享吓一啲聽完個心唔憤氣既說話<br />\n<br />\n我先<br />\n<blockquote>做得仲衰過香港政府 </blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母攞我同香港政府比<br />\n<br />\n希望有巴絲互相分享恥笑吓<br />\n<br />\n利申就黎失業半年<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcecde6f2e05ef888bb1e0dd49fea164938399a2","tid":2008074,"uid":47169,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T18:09:48.000Z","msg":"屌你呢句野真係會令人柒到想搵窿捐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba8112a5da3b6aa28e1d3fc1c7d11cab07eb30ce","tid":2008074,"uid":126046,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T18:26:20.000Z","msg":"仲有一個同事做做吓野發皮氣<br />\n大嘈大叫<br />\n<br />\n有個老細屌鳩佢<br />\n<blockquote>控制唔到自己就轉行當差啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原來同路人黎"},{"pid":"5af14d2d2443b4250d7957a853e7aaa8913379b1","tid":2008074,"uid":2419,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"ba8112a5da3b6aa28e1d3fc1c7d11cab07eb30ce","tid":2008074,"uid":126046,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T18:26:20.000Z","msg":"仲有一個同事做做吓野發皮氣<br />\n大嘈大叫<br />\n<br />\n有個老細屌鳩佢<br />\n<blockquote>控制唔到自己就轉行當差啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原來同路人黎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T18:27:40.000Z","msg":"你老細幾幽默<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a63f88d4164bc10b974b2a80521385d67b825009","tid":2008074,"uid":71199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5af14d2d2443b4250d7957a853e7aaa8913379b1","tid":2008074,"uid":2419,"like":8,"dislike":0,"sc